                            <h1> Welcome to We Collect Your IT</h1>
                            <p>We offer a free collection service across the UK for the removal 
                                of your old IT systems. We safely reuse this equipment by ensuring 
                                any sensitive or personal information that was on these machines is 
                                either physically removed or destroyed before we reuse them. Using us 
                                shall not only benfit the environment by avoiding the waste and disposal
                                 of this equiment but shall also help others, as we donate and proportion of all the 
                                 equipment we collect.
